      </FaqItem>
      <FaqItem question="What if it rains?">
        The event runs rain or shine. It's historically 50/50 on weather. This is the Pacific
        Northwest. Pack a rain shell, bring layers, and embrace it.
      </FaqItem>
      <FaqItem question="Do I need to be an Evergreen member?">
        Nope, everyone is welcome. Members save $25 on registration though, and your trails depend
        on the Evergreen Mountain Bike Alliance. Basic membership is $50/year and pays for itself at
        events like this. <a
          href="https://www.evergreenmtb.org/support-us/become-a-member"
