      </FaqItem>
      <FaqItem id="faq-food" question="What food are you serving? Any veggie/vegan options?">
        Pulled pork sandwich with slaw, pickle, and mango salsa. Side of baked beans, cookie, and
        chips. Plenty of sodas available on site too. We don't have veggie or vegan options planned
